OL,3,C60% of all electric blankets tested by
OL,4,Ccouncil found to be unsafe
OL,6,FMore than 150 electric blankets have
OL,7,Fbeen deemed unsafe by Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FCounty Council - and some of the
OL,9,Fdangerous blankets tested were found
OL,10,Fto be more than 50 years old.
OL,12,F282 electric blankets were tested at
OL,13,Fevents in Cotgrave, Newark and Retford
OL,14,Flast week.
OL,16,FThe council also found most of the
OL,17,Funsafe blankets were more than 10
OL,18,Fyears old.
OL,20,FHere's 10 signs your blanket may not
OL,21,Fbe safe to use:
