OL,4,Ccouncil found to be unsafe
OL,6,FThe council warns you shouldn't just
OL,7,Fthrow the blankets away but take them
OL,8,Fto a household waste and recycling
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FThey are holding their next blanket
OL,12,Ftesting event on Monday 2 December at
OL,13,FAshfield Library.
OL,15,FIf your blanket is found to be
OL,16,Fdangerous, the council say they'll
OL,17,Freplace it with a new one.
